name: mijinko jumper: Daphnia! Fly high!
description:
It is a game to fly Daphnia and aim for a high place.

How to play
Drag the screen to fly the daphnia
Let's aim for a higher place!
If it falls, the game is over!

World ranking support
When you connect to Game Center or Google play game servies
You can challenge the world ranking!
Let's aim for the world champion!
